    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >古代盗马术</h2>《Hustlerix》是一款俯视角开放世界动作游戏。你将扮演高卢人，成为一名高卢英雄，在逆境的严酷考验下成长。你将跃入细节惊人且灵感源自古罗马的等距视图世界，感受生机勃勃的风景、熙熙攘攘的城市及危机重重的竞技场。去挑战腐败议会的权威，将你的成就刻入这个史诗般伟大的时期。有一股神秘力量正在暗中操控历史的进程，而你命中注定要去揭露其背后的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/3da920b2f2d5b1540b35f871f9480aa6.poster.avif?t=1768910478\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/3da920b2f2d5b1540b35f871f9480aa6.webm?t=1768910478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/3da920b2f2d5b1540b35f871f9480aa6.mp4?t=1768910478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >猎杀魔兽</h2>体验引人入胜的对话，其中不时出现的哲学辩论将会考验你的知识储备和诡辩之才。在不公的法律面前挺身而出，将坏人用乱石砸死以保公正，打败来自古罗马神话中的残暴魔兽。你将在旅途中遇见臭名昭著的牛头怪、冷酷无情的九头蛇及其它许多魔兽，逐渐成长为真正的传奇。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/6f8e56739f3a311205545c712fc9391e.poster.avif?t=1768910478\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/6f8e56739f3a311205545c712fc9391e.webm?t=1768910478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/6f8e56739f3a311205545c712fc9391e.mp4?t=1768910478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握战争的艺术</h2>在对战罗马士兵的过程中打磨你的战斗技巧，使用强大的对战系统，战略决策及考验反应能力的动作都包含其中。你将在古罗马角斗场中浸透鲜血的沙砾上与凶猛的角斗士搏斗，在激动人心的战车赛中称王称霸，并向胆敢挑战你的敌人投掷巨石。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/c229a69475aa9c3acb690fcc025f3ee2.poster.avif?t=1768910478\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/c229a69475aa9c3acb690fcc025f3ee2.webm?t=1768910478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/c229a69475aa9c3acb690fcc025f3ee2.mp4?t=1768910478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >引领自己的命运</h2>踏上激动人心的探险，在这个无情的世界中前行，完成一个更比一个艰险的任务。你将对峙臭名昭著的历史人物，智取狡猾的小偷，战胜巡逻的士兵。成为一名声名狼藉的盗马贼，释放自己反叛的一面吧，你也可以将你的怒火瞄准腐败且腰缠万贯的富豪，将他们的财富分给更有需要的人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/90227252e1453ea1e3bedecb33750ace.poster.avif?t=1768910478\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/90227252e1453ea1e3bedecb33750ace.webm?t=1768910478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/90227252e1453ea1e3bedecb33750ace.mp4?t=1768910478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在混乱中寻找平静</h2>然而，并非一切都是战争和鲜血。《Hustlerix》还能给你带来更为安静的时刻以供解压。你可以体验古罗马时代的小确幸，可能是在街边小酒馆享受一顿美味的佳肴，也可能是聆听吟游诗人唱出的优美旋律，抑或是在篝火旁与市民谈笑风生。游戏中拥有动态的日夜循环和天气系统，你甚至可以停下脚步去欣赏远处的美景。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/af645d2aa3c8e705bab54663be4c6772.poster.avif?t=1768910478\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/af645d2aa3c8e705bab54663be4c6772.webm?t=1768910478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/af645d2aa3c8e705bab54663be4c6772.mp4?t=1768910478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏拥有模糊了时代边界的讽刺与智慧</h2>在丰富的开放世界中，你的体验将会通过暗藏其中的现代式讽刺得到提升，影射现代世界的主题与古罗马时代的背景无缝衔接。Hustlerix 不只是一个游戏——它是通往旧时代的窗，是充满挑战的哲学旅程，还是对当代直切要害的写照。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/d8956587ed650ff6ba262b19c2b05e95.poster.avif?t=1768910478\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/d8956587ed650ff6ba262b19c2b05e95.webm?t=1768910478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306240/extras/d8956587ed650ff6ba262b19c2b05e95.mp4?t=1768910478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏包含一系列大胆的冒险可以参与，可以面对传奇般的人物，有沉浸式的世界可以探索。《Hustlerix》一定能契合你心中的英雄情结，给你带来难忘的游戏体验。",
